results.name: Distance from nxtprm(n^2) to (n+1)^2 in A144831 is prime.
formula: Terms in this sequence are from A144831 iff the distance from nxtprm n^2 to (n+1)^2 is prime.
example: a(2)=5 because 3^2=9 and 4^2=16. Nxtprm(3^2)=11 and 16-11=5, a prime.
results.author: _Enoch Haga_, Sep 22 2008
